snippet.title: The Good Life Release Date Announcement Trailer (English)
snippet.description:
Welcome to Rainy Woods, the "happiest town in the world”!
SWERY’s New Small-Town Detective Thriller The Good Life launches on October 15th, 2021 on Steam, Nintendo Switch, PlayStationⓇ4, and Xbox One.
